-- **Pulumi/CDK**: Programmatic infrastructure
-- **Ansible/Chef/Puppet**: Configuration management
-- **GitOps**: Flux, ArgoCD for Kubernetes
-
-Start with declarative approaches unless programmatic benefits are clear.
